OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLong-serving lollipop lady 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBeryl retires after 57     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fyears                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, One of the country's longest-serving   
OL,6, lollipop ladies has hung up her hi-vis 
OL,7, jacket after 57 years on duty.         
OL,9,FBeryl Quantrill, 85, became a school   
OL,10,Fcrossing warden in 1964 and spent her  
OL,11,Ffirst 12 years working outside Barcroft
OL,12,FSchool, in Grimsby.                    
OL,14,FShe followed that with a 45-year stint 
OL,15,Fat Queen Mary Avenue Primary School in 
OL,16,FCleethorpes.                           
OL,18,F"I will miss going to school - I've    
OL,19,Falways looked forward to seeing the    
OL,20,Fkids every day," she said.             
